author: Scott Manley
description:
During the launch of Soyuz MS-28 to the ISS the launch pad at Baikonur was severely damaged and will likely be unable to launch Soyuz or Progress spacecraft without massive repairs. This is the only Russian launch site able to send spacecraft to the ISS

As reported by RussianSpaceWeb 
https://www.russianspaceweb.com/baikonur_r7_31.html

author: Scott Manley
description:
Reentry - A Space Flight Simulator has finally reached the 1.0 release with the ability to play through almost all the important moments in the Mercury, Gemini and Apollo programs. And by 'Play' I mean you can follow all the real documentation and checklists to perform the same complex procedures the astronauts needed for these historic flights.

https://store.steampowered.com/app/882140/Reentry__A_Space_Flight_Simulator/
